Nick De Ruiz https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nick_De_Ruiz 0 Nicholas De Ruiz (February, 1871 – 21 June 1959) was an American actor. He appeared in 36 films between 1920 and 1938. He was born in Santa Barbara, California and died in Los Angeles, California, aged 88. Nicholas_De_Ruiz ( February , 1871 – 21_June_1959 ) was an_American_actor .
